DE_COTROCENI

The first official map of the largest CS:GO and CS:S community from ROMANIA

ASTRAMANIA http://forum.astramania.ro

Special thanks to Wicked the owner of Astramania servers and to the Astrateam,for testing and important feedback.

Map created by Septimius A.I.

The map has 64 spawn points,radar view, two bomb sites A (in the basement) B at the second floor.Excelent fps,server tested over 3 months on Astramania servers.

The map depicts a symbolic romanian presidential palace,hence the name Cotroceni,and it does not intend to replicate the original palace.

Have fun! ;)
